    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094540/extras/a693a53e351c6a46e3df55be49b79951.poster.avif?t=1751619362\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094540/extras/a693a53e351c6a46e3df55be49b79951.webm?t=1751619362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094540/extras/a693a53e351c6a46e3df55be49b79951.mp4?t=1751619362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《夏娃战记》是一款动作、策略游戏，包含众多16位游戏时代的经典游戏元素。与火辣潇洒的主角夏娃、和她值得信赖的铠甲伙伴斯莫特，<strong>在轰鸣之地以上帝视角开疆扩土</strong>、<strong>在流畅爽快的横板关卡提升实力</strong>。你将与值得信赖的指挥官们合纵连横；也会在动作关卡里，解锁战斗招式、提升等级，与邪恶的敌人、险恶的环境、强大的敌方首领们斗争到底。一起解放夏娃和斯莫特真正的力量吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094540/extras/5a995cf7776dd67c1ab42b84d89bd2ba.poster.avif?t=1751619362\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094540/extras/5a995cf7776dd67c1ab42b84d89bd2ba.webm?t=1751619362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094540/extras/5a995cf7776dd67c1ab42b84d89bd2ba.mp4?t=1751619362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏故事</h2>在伊甸园意外被毁后，夏娃发现自己被置身于一个未知的世界，她的爱人亚当也不见了踪影。她启程寻找亚当，途中遇见了斯莫特——一头自信过度又话痨的有翼生物。斯莫特具有强大的转化能力，能变身为适合使用者的武装铠甲，有着不可思议的力量。<br><br>斯莫特宣称自己要为夏娃提供“无价”的帮助，两人一起前往危机四伏的轰鸣之地。斯莫特在那里扩张自己的领土，以拓宽搜索范围来寻找亚当的踪迹。期待着能找到安全无恙的亚当，找到回去的方法，回归和平的生活……<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094540/extras/cacd50f8a812afd03efc4756226b0664.poster.avif?t=1751619362\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094540/extras/cacd50f8a812afd03efc4756226b0664.webm?t=1751619362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094540/extras/cacd50f8a812afd03efc4756226b0664.mp4?t=1751619362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特性</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094540/extras/c18283e03fb657514b2be578b15e0c16.webp?t=1751619362\" width=631 height=16 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>多种游戏模式——包括快节奏的横版动作过关和上帝视角策略战。<br></li><li>多彩的世界探索——从地狱到美丽不可方物的仙境，众多场景风格等你来战。<br></li><li>可专精战斗技能——完成多样的挑战来解锁三套战斗动作模式、共计四十种招式升级，学会进阶移动方式、完成战术防御，以应对各式敌人。<br></li><li>激发“熔炼”之力——你可以在战斗时使用它，或在险峻的地形寻物时让它为你指明方向。<br></li><li>富有挑战的2D横板关卡——打败敌人，铲除黑幕，发掘反派们不为人知的故事。<br></li><li>拓展你的领土——利用多种建筑，制造并升级你的军事单位，将版图扩张到多个地区！<br></li><li>完成高难挑战——隐藏的升级路径，高难关卡……<br></li><li>性格鲜明角色——他们有的很狂，有的更狂，有的非常狂。<br></li><li>充满魄力的音乐——由Evader带来的热情吉他和Manami Matsumae所作的片头与片尾乐。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094540/extras/ff36f0707298aca6d2700e47dd2ebe13.poster.avif?t=1751619362\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094540/extras/ff36f0707298aca6d2700e47dd2ebe13.webm?t=1751619362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094540/extras/ff36f0707298aca6d2700e47dd2ebe13.mp4?t=1751619362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
